Recently, the prosecutor's office of the Krasnodar Territory revealed the facts of including unreasonable costs in the tariffs.
And in the expenses of LLC "IV-consulting" (supplies cold water) were laid 4 million rubles. for the rental of cars at a price above the market price.
And there are a lot of such examples in the country.
People give the last money for the "communal services", and pay regularly - according to the Ministry of Construction of the Russian Federation, the average collection of payments from the population is 94%.
