A native of Glasgow Stewart, 55, who I followed from Sister Ray (counting data: two young women, three middle-aged men) to Reckless Records (counting data: eight middle-aged men, one woman probably over 20), in London for half a day to hold a meeting, and walking around the shops to take a few hours.
He's a collector, I ask?
